center gap-1.5 text-[9px] sm:text-[10px] font-black py-1 px-2.5 rounded bg-emerald-500 hover:bg-emerald-400 text-slate-950 cursor-pointer transition-all shadow hover:scale-102\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-map-location-dot animate-pulse\"></i> 🗺️ Bu Konuyu Harita Atlasında İncele</button>",
