MKÜREDE OLMANIN KANITLARI</b><br><b>1. Kanıtlar:</b> Türkiye'nin Kuzey Yarımküre'de (KYK) yer aldığının kesin kanıtları:<br>• Güneyden esen rüzgarların (Lodos, Kıble, Samyeli) sıcaklığı artırması, kuzeyden esenlerin (Karayel, Yıldız, Poyraz) sıcaklığı düşürmesi.<br>• Haziran, Temmuz, Ağustos aylarında yaz, Aralık, Ocak, Şubat aylarında kış mevsimini yaşamamız.<br>• Kuzeye gidildikçe Kutup Yıldızı'nın görünüm açısının büyümesi.<br>• Dağlarımızın güney yamaçlarının bakı etkisinde olması.<br>⚠️ <b>ÖSYM UYARISI:</b> Çizgisel hızın kuzeye doğru azalması sadece KYK'yi değil, kutuplara yaklaşıldığını kanıtlar. Ancak güneyden esen rüzgarların sıcaklığı artırması sadece KYK'ye özgüdür.",
      "MutlakKonum": "\n<div class=\"relative group my-3 mx-auto w-full max-w-[360px]\">\n    <svg class=\"w-full h-auto shadow-lg rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950/60 p-2 block transition-all\" viewBox=\"0 0 500 220\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" id=\"inline-svg-57784515\">\n      <defs>\n        <clipPath id=\"turkey-clip-path-inline-svg-57784515\">\n          <path d=\"M 35,78 L 32,50 L 70,45 Q 95,52 115,60 L 145,62 Q 165,58 190,58 Q 225,62 260,50 Q 280,62 295,65 Q 310,60 325,66 Q 370,72 415,60 L 440,70 L 480,90 L 460,115 L 470,135 L 460,155 L 415,168 L 350,165 L 290,165 L 265,170 L 260,185 L 250,180 L 248,162 Q 215,155 170,176 Q 140,155 110,158 L 85,175 Q 65,150 50,150 Q 35,138 45,130 Q 32,120 40,110 Q 30,100 45,92 L 32,85 Z\" />\n        </clipPath>\n        <marker id=\"arrow-marker-blue\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto-start-reverse\">\n          <path d=\"M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z\" fill=\"#3b82f6\"/>\n        </marker>\n        <marker id=\"arrow-marker-red\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto-start-reverse\">\n          <path d=\"M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z\" fill=\"#f43f5e\"/>\n        </marker>\n        <marker id=\"arrow-marker-purple\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto-start-reverse\">\n          <path d=\"M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z\" fill=\"#818cf8\"/>\n        </marker>\n      </defs>\n    <g clip-path=\"url(#turkey-clip-path-inline-svg-57784515)\"><path d=\"M 35,78 L 32,50 L 70,45 Q 95,52 115,60 L 145,62 Q 165,58 190,58 Q 225,62 260,50 Q 280,62 295,65 Q 310,60 325,66 Q 370,72 415,60 L 440,70 L 480,90 L 460,115 L 470,135 L 460,155 L 415,168 L 350,165 L 290,165 L 265,170 L 260,185 L 250,180 L 248,162 Q 215,155 170,176 Q 140,155 110,158 L 85,175 Q 65,150 50,150 Q 35,138 45,130 Q 32,120 40,110 Q 30,100 45,92 L 32,85 Z\" fill=\"#111827\" stroke=\"#334155\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" /></g>\n  <!-- Siyasi Kara Sınırları Çizgileri -->\n  <g stroke=\"#6366f1\" stroke-width=\"1.2\" stroke-dasharray=\"3 2\" opacity=\"0.8\" fill=\"none\">\n    <path d=\"M 35,78 L 32,50\" />\n    <path d=\"M 32,50 L 70,45\" />\n    <path d=\"M 415,60 L 440,70\" />\n    <path d=\"M 440,70 L 480,90\" />\n    <path d=\"M 480,90 L 460,115 L 470,135 L 460,155\" />\n    <path d=\"M 460,155 L 415,168\" />\n    <path d=\"M 415,168 L 350,165 L 290,165 L 265,170 L 260,185\" />\n  </g>\n  \n  <!-- Komşu Ülke İsim Etiketleri -->\n  <g id=\"neighbor-labels\" opacity=\"0.45\" pointer-events=\"none\" font-family=\"sans-serif\" font-weight=\"900\" font-size=\"5.5\" fill=\"#94a3b8\">\n    <text x=\"12\" y=\"66\" text-anchor=\"middle\">YUNANİSTAN</text>\n    <text x=\"36\" y=\"38\" text-anchor=\"middle\">BULGARİSTAN</text>\n    <text x=\"442\" y=\"52\">GÜRCİSTAN</text>\n    <text x=\"475\" y=\"78\">ERMENİSTAN</text>\n    <text x=\"480\" y=\"125\">İRAN</text>\n    <text x=\"432\" y=\"180\">IRAK</text>\n    <text x=\"310\" y=\"188\">SURİYE</text>\n  </g>\n<circle cx=\"100\" cy=\"160\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"170\" cy=\"170\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"230\" cy=\"155\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"390\" cy=\"85\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"260\" cy=\"62\" r=\"7\" fill=\"#10b981\" stroke=\"#ffffff\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" /><text x=\"260\" y=\"51\" fill=\"#ffffff\" font-size=\"8.5\" font-weight=\"black\" font-family=\"sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" background-color=\"#0f172a\" filter=\"drop-shadow(0px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.9))\">Sinop</text><circle cx=\"75\" cy=\"55\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"50\" cy=\"155\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"205\" cy=\"115\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"450\" cy=\"135\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"115\" cy=\"65\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"295\" cy=\"70\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"85\" cy=\"172\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"45\" cy=\"115\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"270\" cy=\"125\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"430\" cy=\"85\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"55\" cy=\"75\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"195\" cy=\"65\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"360\" cy=\"155\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"330\" cy=\"110\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"260\" cy=\"165\" r=\"7\" fill=\"#10b981\" stroke=\"#ffffff\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" /><text x=\"260\" y=\"154\" fill=\"#ffffff\" font-size=\"8.5\" font-weight=\"black\" font-family=\"sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" background-color=\"#0f172a\" filter=\"drop-shadow(0px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.9))\">İskenderun</text></svg>\n    <button onclick=\"openNoteZoomModal('MutlakKonum')\" class=\"absolute top-2 right-2 opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100 bg-slate-950/90 hover:bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 text-[9px] font-black py-1 px-2.5 rounded-lg text-emerald-400 cursor-pointer transition-all shadow hover:scale-105 flex items-center gap-1 z-10\" title=\"Ders Notunu Tam Ekran Oku\">\n        <i class=\"fa-solid fa-expand animate-pulse\"></i> 🔍 TAM EKRAN OKU\n    </button>\n</div>\n<br><b>TÜRKİYE'NİN MUTLAK (MATEMATİKSEL) KONUMU</b><br><b>1. Koordinatlar:</b> Türkiye, <b>36° - 42° Kuzey Enlemleri</b> ile <b>26° - 45° Doğu Boylamları</b> arasında yer alır.<br>• En kuzeyi ile en güneyi arasında 6 enlem derecesi (666 km kuş uçuşu mesafe) vardır.<br>• En doğusu ile en batısı arasında 19 boylam derecesi (76 dakikalık zaman farkı) vardır.<br><b>2. Sonuçları:</b> Orta kuşakta yer alır, kuzeyden esen rüzgarlar sıcaklığı düşürürken güneyden esenler artırır, gölge yönü yıl boyunca kuzeyi gösterir, güneş ışınları hiçbir zaman 90 derecelik dik açıyla gelmez (gölge boyu asla sıfır olmaz).<br>⚠️ <b>ÖSYM UYARISI:</b> Türkiye'de gölge yönünün yıl boyunca sadece kuzeyi göstermesi, Türkiye'nin <b>Yengeç Dönencesi'nin kuzeyinde</b> yer almasının doğrudan bir sonucudur.",
      "OrtaKuşakKanıtı": "\n<div class=\"relative group my-3 mx-auto w-full max-w-[360px]\">\n    <svg class=\"w-full h-auto shadow-lg rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950/60 p-2 block transition-all\" viewBox=\"0 0 500 220\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" id=\"inline-svg-38334784\">\n      <defs>\n        <clipPath id=\"turkey-clip-path-inline-svg-38334784\">\n          <path d=\"M 35,78 L 32,50 L 70,45 Q 95,52 115,60 L 145,62 Q 165,58 190,58 Q 225,62 260,50 Q 280,62 295,65 Q 310,60 325,66 Q 370,72 415,60 L 440,70 L 480,90 L 460,115 L 470,135 L 460,155 L 415,168 L 350,165 L 290,165 L 265,170 L 260,185 L 250,180 L 248,162 Q 215,155 170,176 Q 140,155 110,158 L 85,175 Q 65,150 50,150 Q 35,138 45,130 Q 32,120 40,110 Q 30,100 45,92 L 32,85 Z\" />\n        </clipPath>\n        <marker id=\"arrow-marker-blue\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto-start-reverse\">\n          <path d=\"M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z\" fill=\"#3b82f6\"/>\n        </marker>\n        <marker id=\"arrow-marker-red\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto-start-reverse\">\n          <path d=\"M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z\" fill=\"#f43f5e\"/>\n        </marker>\n        <marker id=\"arrow-marker-purple\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto-start-reverse\">\n          <path d=\"M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z\" fill=\"#818cf8\"/>\n        </marker>\n      </defs>\n    <g clip-path=\"url(#turkey-clip-path-inline-svg-38334784)\"><path d=\"M 35,78 L 32,50 L 70,45 Q 95,52 115,60 L 145,62 Q 165,58 190,58 Q 225,62 260,50 Q 280,62 295,65 Q 310,60 325,66 Q 370,72 415,60 L 440,70 L 480,90 L 460,115 L 470,135 L 460,155 L 415,168 L 350,165 L 290,165 L 265,170 L 260,185 L 250,180 L 248,162 Q 215,155 170,176 Q 140,155 110,158 L 85,175 Q 65,150 50,150 Q 35,138 45,130 Q 32,120 40,110 Q 30,100 45,92 L 32,85 Z\" fill=\"#111827\" stroke=\"#334155\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" /></g>\n  <!-- Siyasi Kara Sınırları Çizgileri -->\n  <g stroke=\"#6366f1\" stroke-width=\"1.2\" stroke-dasharray=\"3 2\" opacity=\"0.8\" fill=\"none\">\n    <path d=\"M 35,78 L 32,50\" />\n    <path d=\"M 32,50 L 70,45\" />\n    <path d=\"M 415,60 L 440,70\" />\n    <path d=\"M 440,70 L 480,90\" />\n    <path d=\"M 480,90 L 460,115 L 470,135 L 460,155\" />\n    <path d=\"M 460,155 L 415,168\" />\n    <path d=\"M 415,168 L 350,165 L 290,165 L 265,170 L 260,185\" />\n  </g>\n  \n  <!-- Komşu Ülke İsim Etiketleri -->\n  <g id=\"neighbor-labels\" opacity=\"0.45\" pointer-events=\"none\" font-family=\"sans-serif\" font-weight=\"900\" font-size=\"5.5\" fill=\"#94a3b8\">\n    <text x=\"12\" y=\"66\" text-anchor=\"middle\">YUNANİSTAN</text>\n    <text x=\"36\" y=\"38\" text-anchor=\"middle\">BULGARİSTAN</text>\n    <text x=\"442\" y=\"52\">GÜRCİSTAN</text>\n    <text x=\"475\" y=\"78\">ERMENİSTAN</text>\n    <text x=\"480\" y=\"125\">İRAN</text>\n    <text x=\"432\" y=\"180\">IRAK</text>\n    <text x=\"310\" y=\"188\">SURİYE</text>\n  </g>\n\n      <text x=\"250\" y=\"35\" fill=\"#10b981\" font-size=\"9.5\" font-weight=\"black\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"sans-serif\">TÜRKİYE ORTA KUŞAKTADIR (A-B-C-D Kanıtları) 🌍</text>\n      <text x=\"250\" y=\"110\" fill=\"#34d399\" font-size=\"8\" font-weight=\"bold\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"sans-serif\">A - Akdeniz İklim kuşağındayız</text>\n      <text x=\"250\" y=\"125\" fill=\"#34d399\" font-size=\"8\" font-weight=\"bold\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"sans-serif\">B - Batı Rüzgarları etkisindeyiz</text>\n      <text x=\"250\" y=\"140\" fill=\"#34d399\" font-size=\"8\" font-weight=\"bold\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"sans-serif\">C - Cephe Yağışları (Frontal) görülür</text>\n      <text x=\"250\" y=\"155\" fill=\"#34d399\" font-size=\"8\" font-weight=\"bold\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"sans-serif\">D - Dört Mevsim belirgin yaşanır</text>\n    <circle cx=\"100\" cy=\"160\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"170\" cy=\"170\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"230\" cy=\"155\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"390\" cy=\"85\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"260\" cy=\"62\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"75\" cy=\"55\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"50\" cy=\"155\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"205\" cy=\"115\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"450\" cy=\"135\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"115\" cy=\"65\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"295\" cy=\"70\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"85\" cy=\"172\" r=\"7\" fill=\"#10b981\" stroke=\"#ffffff\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" /><text x=\"85\" y=\"161\" fill=\"#ffffff\" font-size=\"8.5\" font-weight=\"black\" font-family=\"sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" background-color=\"#0f172a\" filter=\"drop-shadow(0px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.9))\">Kaş</text><circle cx=\"45\" cy=\"115\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"270\" cy=\"125\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"430\" cy=\"85\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"55\" cy=\"75\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"195\" cy=\"65\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"360\" cy=\"155\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"330\" cy=\"110\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"260\" cy=\"165\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /></svg>\n    <button onclick=\"openNoteZoomModal('OrtaKuşakKanıtı')\" class=\"absolute top-2 right-2 opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100 bg-slate-950/90 hover:bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 text-[9px] font-black py-1 px-2.5 rounded-lg text-emerald-400 cursor-pointer transition-all shadow hover:scale-105 flex items-center gap-1 z-10\" title=\"Ders Notunu Tam Ekran Oku\">\n        <i class=\"fa-solid fa-expand animate-pulse\"></i> 🔍 TAM EKRAN OKU\n    </button>\n</div>\n<br><b>TÜRKİYE'NİN ORTA KUŞAKTA OLMASININ KANITLARI (A-B-C-D)</b><br>Türkiye'nin Orta Kuşakta (30° - 60° enlemleri arasında) yer aldığını kanıtlayan 4 temel coğrafi olay vardır. Bunlar <b>A-B-C-D formülü</b> ile ezberlenir:<br>• <b>A - Akdeniz İklimi:</b> Türkiye'nin Akdeniz iklim kuşağında bulunması ve buna bağlı maki bitki örtüsü ile terra rossa topraklarının görülmesi.<br>• <b>B - Batı Rüzgarları:</b> Yıl boyunca esen sürekli rüzgarlardan Batı rüzgarlarının etkisi altında olması.<br>• <b>C - Cephesel Yağışlar (Frontal):</b> Sıcak ekvatoral hava ile soğuk kutupsal havanın Türkiye üzerinde karşılaşarak cephe yağışları oluşturması.<br>• <b>D - Dört Mevsim:</b> Yıl içinde 4 mevsimin (İlkbahar, Yaz, Sonbahar, Kış) belirgin olarak, arka arkaya yaşanması.<br>⚠️ <b>ÖSYM DETAYI:</b> 'Yıl içinde 4 mevsimin belirgin yaşanması' matematiksel konumdur (orta kuşak). Ancak 'Aynı anda farklı iklim özelliklerinin yaşanması' özel konumdur (yükselti ve yerşekilleri).<br><button onclick=\"showConceptOnMap('iklim')\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[9px] sm:text-[10px] font-black py-1 px-2.5 rounded bg-emerald-500 hover:bg-emerald-400 text-slate-950 cursor-pointer transition-all shadow hover:scale-102\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-map-location-dot animate-pulse\"></i> 🗺️ Bu Konuyu Harita Atlasında İncele</button>",
