e-width=\"1.5\" /><rect x=\"30\" y=\"40\" width=\"440\" height=\"42\" fill=\"#10b981\" opacity=\"0.3\" /></g>\n  <!-- Siyasi Kara Sınırları Çizgileri -->\n  <g stroke=\"#6366f1\" stroke-width=\"1.2\" stroke-dasharray=\"3 2\" opacity=\"0.8\" fill=\"none\">\n    <path d=\"M 35,78 L 32,50\" />\n    <path d=\"M 32,50 L 70,45\" />\n    <path d=\"M 415,60 L 440,70\" />\n    <path d=\"M 440,70 L 480,90\" />\n    <path d=\"M 480,90 L 460,115 L 470,135 L 460,155\" />\n    <path d=\"M 460,155 L 415,168\" />\n    <path d=\"M 415,168 L 350,165 L 290,165 L 265,170 L 260,185\" />\n  </g>\n  \n  <!-- Komşu Ülke İsim Etiketleri -->\n  <g id=\"neighbor-labels\" opacity=\"0.45\" pointer-events=\"none\" font-family=\"sans-serif\" font-weight=\"900\" font-size=\"5.5\" fill=\"#94a3b8\">\n    <text x=\"12\" y=\"66\" text-anchor=\"middle\">YUNANİSTAN</text>\n    <text x=\"36\" y=\"38\" text-anchor=\"middle\">BULGARİSTAN</text>\n    <text x=\"442\" y=\"52\">GÜRCİSTAN</text>\n    <text x=\"475\" y=\"78\">ERMENİSTAN</text>\n    <text x=\"480\" y=\"125\">İRAN</text>\n    <text x=\"432\" y=\"180\">IRAK</text>\n    <text x=\"310\" y=\"188\">SURİYE</text>\n  </g>\n<circle cx=\"100\" cy=\"160\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"170\" cy=\"170\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"230\" cy=\"155\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"390\" cy=\"85\" r=\"7\" fill=\"#10b981\" stroke=\"#ffffff\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" /><text x=\"390\" y=\"74\" fill=\"#ffffff\" font-size=\"8.5\" font-weight=\"black\" font-family=\"sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" background-color=\"#0f172a\" filter=\"drop-shadow(0px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.9))\">Trabzon-Rize-Artvin</text><circle cx=\"260\" cy=\"62\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"75\" cy=\"55\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"50\" cy=\"155\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"205\" cy=\"115\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"450\" cy=\"135\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"115\" cy=\"65\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"295\" cy=\"70\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"85\" cy=\"172\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"45\" cy=\"115\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"270\" cy=\"125\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"430\" cy=\"85\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"55\" cy=\"75\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"195\" cy=\"65\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"360\" cy=\"155\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"330\" cy=\"110\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"260\" cy=\"165\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /></svg>\n    <button onclick=\"openNoteZoomModal('Karadenizİklimi')\" class=\"absolute top-2 right-2 opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100 bg-slate-950/90 hover:bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 text-[9px] font-black py-1 px-2.5 rounded-lg text-emerald-400 cursor-pointer transition-all shadow hover:scale-105 flex items-center gap-1 z-10\" title=\"Ders Notunu Tam Ekran Oku\">\n        <i class=\"fa-solid fa-expand animate-pulse\"></i> 🔍 TAM EKRAN OKU\n    </button>\n</div>\n<br><b>KARADENİZ İKLİMİ VE KAHVERENGİ ORMAN TOPRAĞI</b><br><b>1. İklim Karakteri:</b> Her mevsim yağışlı, ılıman denizeldir. En fazla yağışı sonbaharda (yamaç yağışları - orografik) alır. Nemlilik fazla olduğu için yıllık ve günlük sıcaklık farkları Türkiye'de en az olan iklimdir.<br><b>2. Toprak ve Bitki:</b> Karakteristik toprağı aşırı yıkanmış, humusça zengin <b>Kahverengi Orman Toprağı</b>'dır. Bitki örtüsü kıyıda geniş yapraklı gür ormanlar, yükseklerde iğne yapraklılar ve dağ çayırlarıdır.<br>⚠️ <b>ÖSYM UYARISI:</b> Karadeniz'de her mevsim yağışlı olduğu için <b>tarımda nadas ihtiyacı yoktur</b>. Güneşli gün sayısı en az olan iklimimizdir, bu yüzden güneş enerjisi potansiyeli çok düşüktür.<br><button onclick=\"showConceptOnMap('iklim')\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[9px] sm:text-[10px] font-black py-1 px-2.5 rounded bg-emerald-500 hover:bg-emerald-400 text-slate-950 cursor-pointer transition-all shadow hover:scale-102\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-map-location-dot animate-pulse\"></i> 🗺️ Bu Konuyu Harita Atlasında İncele</button>",
