 opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"295\" cy=\"70\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"85\" cy=\"172\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"45\" cy=\"115\" r=\"7\" fill=\"#10b981\" stroke=\"#ffffff\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" /><text x=\"45\" y=\"104\" fill=\"#ffffff\" font-size=\"8.5\" font-weight=\"black\" font-family=\"sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" background-color=\"#0f172a\" filter=\"drop-shadow(0px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.9))\">İzmir-Manisa-Aydın</text><circle cx=\"270\" cy=\"125\" r=\"7\" fill=\"#10b981\" stroke=\"#ffffff\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" /><text x=\"270\" y=\"114\" fill=\"#ffffff\" font-size=\"8.5\" font-weight=\"black\" font-family=\"sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" background-color=\"#0f172a\" filter=\"drop-shadow(0px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.9))\">Konya-Ankara-Kayseri</text><circle cx=\"430\" cy=\"85\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"55\" cy=\"75\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"195\" cy=\"65\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"360\" cy=\"155\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"330\" cy=\"110\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"260\" cy=\"165\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /></svg>\n    <button onclick=\"openNoteZoomModal('BorMaden')\" class=\"absolute top-2 right-2 opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100 bg-slate-950/90 hover:bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 text-[9px] font-black py-1 px-2.5 rounded-lg text-emerald-400 cursor-pointer transition-all shadow hover:scale-105 flex items-center gap-1 z-10\" title=\"Ders Notunu Tam Ekran Oku\">\n        <i class=\"fa-solid fa-expand animate-pulse\"></i> 🔍 TAM EKRAN OKU\n    </button>\n</div>\n<br><br><b>BOR MİNERALLERİ VE REZERV LİDERLİĞİ</b><br>\n<b>1. Özelliği:</b> Türkiye dünya bor rezervinin yaklaşık **%72'sine** sahip olarak tartışmasız liderdir. Roket yakıtı, cam, çimento, deterjan ve nükleer sanayide kullanılır.<br>\n<b>2. Çıkarıldığı Yerler (Kritik Havzalar):</b><br>\n• <b>Balıkesir:</b> Bigadiç, Susurluk.<br>\n• <b>Kütahya:</b> Emet.<br>\n• <b>Eskişehir:</b> Kırka.<br>\n• <b>Bursa:</b> Mustafakemalpaşa.<br>\n<b>3. İşlendiği Yerler:</b> <b>Bandırma Boraks Fabrikası (Balıkesir)</b> (Liman/ihracat kolaylığı) ve **Kırka (Eskişehir)**.",
