5569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"295\" cy=\"70\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"85\" cy=\"172\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"45\" cy=\"115\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"270\" cy=\"125\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"430\" cy=\"85\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"55\" cy=\"75\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"195\" cy=\"65\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"360\" cy=\"155\" r=\"7\" fill=\"#10b981\" stroke=\"#ffffff\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" /><text x=\"360\" y=\"144\" fill=\"#ffffff\" font-size=\"8.5\" font-weight=\"black\" font-family=\"sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" background-color=\"#0f172a\" filter=\"drop-shadow(0px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.9))\">Şanlıurfa-Mardin-Diyarbakır</text><circle cx=\"330\" cy=\"110\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /><circle cx=\"260\" cy=\"165\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"#475569\" opacity=\"0.4\" pointer-events=\"none\" /></svg>\n    <button onclick=\"openNoteZoomModal('PetrolEnerjisi')\" class=\"absolute top-2 right-2 opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100 bg-slate-950/90 hover:bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 text-[9px] font-black py-1 px-2.5 rounded-lg text-emerald-400 cursor-pointer transition-all shadow hover:scale-105 flex items-center gap-1 z-10\" title=\"Ders Notunu Tam Ekran Oku\">\n        <i class=\"fa-solid fa-expand animate-pulse\"></i> 🔍 TAM EKRAN OKU\n    </button>\n</div>\n<br><br><b>PETROL ÜRETİMİ VE RAFİNERİLER</b><br>\n<b>1. Özelliği:</b> Türkiye petrol ihtiyacının yaklaşık %90'ını ithal eder. Üretim sadece Şanlıurfa-Mardin-Diyarbakır Anadolu'da yapılır. İlk yatak 1940'ta <b>Batman Raman</b>'da bulunmuştur.<br>\n<b>2. Petrol Rafinerilerimiz:</b><br>\n• <b>Batman Rafinerisi:</b> Hammaddeye yakın kurulan tek ve en küçük rafineridir.<br>\n• <b>İzmit İpraş Rafinerisi:</b> Ulaşım ve tüketim merkezine yakınlık.<br>\n• <b>İzmir Aliağa Rafinerisi:</b> Liman ve ihracat kolaylığı (kıyıda).<br>\n• <b>Mersin Ataş Rafinerisi:</b> Depolama ve liman (kıyıda).<br>\n• <b>Kırıkkale Orta Anadolu Rafinerisi:</b> Güvenli iç bölge (askeri gerekçeler) ve pazar yakınlığı (boru hatlarıyla bağlanır).",
